<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>movie theater • moving theater</xh5><p> <i>movie theater—</i>a building where movies are shown to an audience; a cinema: When we go to a <u>movie theater</u> today, we experience a much different world than the theater-goer of the early twentieth century.</p><p> <i>moving theater—</i>virtual reality simulator with seats moving where you actually ride with the movie and experience every bump, dip and turn: How am I to eat and drink in a <u>moving theater</u> seat tossing me around for two hours.</p> </entry>
